            <div type="edition" subtype="primary" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="grc" resp="#JP" source="#autopsy">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost">ἐν</supplied>ταῦθα <choice><orig>τ</orig><reg>κ</reg></choice>ῖτε
                    <lb n="2"/><g ref="#staurogram">&#x101a0;</g>
                    <lb n="3"/><persName type="attested"><name>Σωτηρὴς</name></persName> γ<choice><orig>οι</orig><reg>υ</reg></choice>νή
                    <lb n="4"/><persName type="attested"><name>Ἡρακλίωνος</name></persName> τοῦ
                    <lb n="5"/><choice><orig>οἱπ</orig><reg>ἱππ</reg></choice>οιατροῦ
                </ab>
                </div>
            <div type="apparatus" resp="#JP">
                <listApp><app><note>Text based upon autopsy</note></app></listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>Here lies Soteres, wife of Heraklion the veterinarian</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The form of the name Soteres is probably for Soteris.</p>
            </div>
